ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip

Class ActionMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip.ActionMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message, java.io.Serializable

    public class ActionMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Message
    This class acts as container for messages used either to perform updates from a Frontend to a ReplicationManager or for a ReplicationManager to answer a request from a Frontend.
    Author:
    sosterwalder
